title: List of Palestine international footballers born outside Palestine
text:
This is a list of football players who represented the <a href="Palestine%20national%20football%20team">Palestine national football team</a> in international <a href="association%20football">football</a> and were "born outside the <a href="State%20of%20Palestine">State of Palestine</a>".
The following players:
This list includes players who have <a href="Multiple%20citizenship">dual citizenship</a> with Palestine and/or have become <a href="naturalization">naturalized</a> Palestinian citizens. The players are ordered per modern-day country of birth; if the country at the time of birth differs from the current, this is indicated with a subsection.
